# Environment Variables Template

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values.

## Network Configuration
BASE_RPC_URL=https://mainnet.base.org
BASE_CHAIN_ID=8453

## Token Configuration
TOKEN_NAME=xTesT
TOKEN_SYMBOL=XTEST
TOKEN_MAX_SUPPLY=1000000000
TOKEN_PUBLIC_CAP=500000000
